WEBVTT

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:35.800
Father, Mother.

00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:39.340
This is the restaurant you both worked so hard to build.

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:41.400
I've finally avenged you.

00:01:57.720 --> 00:01:58.600
Husband.

00:01:58.759 --> 00:02:02.360
You didn't take your medicine last night. You must take it today.

00:02:03.960 --> 00:02:06.220
Why have you been so kind to me these days?

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.160
What are you saying?

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:10.600
I am your wife.

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:12.850
It's only right that I take care of you.

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:17.120
But I took you away from Sinan.

00:02:18.480 --> 00:02:19.940
Don't you hate me anymore?

00:02:23.040 --> 00:02:24.170
It's all in the past.

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:30.360
If I said I don't want to drink this bitter medicine...

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:32.480
Would you believe me?

00:02:32.720 --> 00:02:34.440
But you're sick.

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:39.970
If a healthy person takes these medicines every day,

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:42.340
wouldn't they actually become sick?

00:02:43.160 --> 00:02:45.320
I think your fever has made you delirious.

00:02:45.320 --> 00:02:47.120
Hurry up and take your medicine.

00:02:47.520 --> 00:02:49.450
You can't take it when it gets cold.

00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:12.840
Ah.

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:21.400
Will you always be this good to me?

00:03:23.760 --> 00:03:24.840
Don't overthink.

00:03:25.480 --> 00:03:26.600
Go to sleep now.

00:03:36.840 --> 00:03:37.960
Go report to the master quickly.

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:39.820
Let's call a doctor to take a look.

00:03:40.240 --> 00:03:41.560
Get back here!

00:03:42.240 --> 00:03:44.960
If any of you leak a word about this,

00:03:45.240 --> 00:03:47.840
I'll have your heads. Now get out!

00:03:55.320 --> 00:03:57.780
Manager Zhang, you're here. Please come in.

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:00.700
Since my parents passed away,

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:03.320
the restaurant hasn't been able to recreate that taste.

00:04:03.320 --> 00:04:05.320
Business has slowed down considerably.

00:04:05.320 --> 00:04:06.520
But today...

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:28.560
Madam.

00:04:29.400 --> 00:04:30.860
Where is your invitation?

00:04:32.840 --> 00:04:33.880
Invitation.

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:34.760
Yes.

00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:35.960
Don't you know?

00:04:35.960 --> 00:04:39.840
Today is a joyous occasion as the Liu family's second young master takes over the restaurant.

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:42.840
It's also the day of his engagement to Miss Xu.

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:44.650
It's a double celebration!

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:48.960
Everyone, please enjoy the food and drinks.

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:50.040
Certainly.

00:04:53.880 --> 00:04:55.960
Shuyun, let me introduce you to someone.

00:04:55.960 --> 00:04:59.159
This is Mr. Sun from the neighboring chamber of commerce.

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:02.040
Madam! Madam!

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:04.360
You can't enter without an invitation.

00:05:08.440 --> 00:05:11.040
Yiyu, why didn't you tell me you were coming?

00:05:11.320 --> 00:05:12.560
I couldn't find you these past few days.

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:13.840
How could I tell you?

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:18.040
I've been extremely busy lately.

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:20.020
I forgot to introduce you.

00:05:20.680 --> 00:05:22.240
This is the daughter of Yuncheng Commander,

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:23.480
Miss Xu Shuyun.

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:26.880
Shuyun, this is Miss Qian Yiyu.

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:29.280
So she's Miss Xu Qian Yiyu, who broke off the engagement with Liu Silin.

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:30.280
Hello there.

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:34.000
Is this the maid from the Liu household you mentioned?

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.480
Who are you calling a maid?

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:39.720
Isn't a housekeeper's daughter just a maid?

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:41.760
Am I wrong, Sinan?

00:05:44.840 --> 00:05:46.320
Sinan.

00:05:46.840 --> 00:05:49.040
Such an intimate way of addressing him.

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:53.000
Even a commander's daughter can be so frivolous.

00:05:53.159 --> 00:05:54.890
Who are you calling frivolous?

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:58.000
Such nerve from a mere maid.

00:05:58.280 --> 00:05:59.159
Yiyu.

00:05:59.840 --> 00:06:01.160
We're in public.

00:06:01.720 --> 00:06:03.000
Stop making a scene.

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:04.440
I will.

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:09.880
You must be jealous that I can marry Sinan.

00:06:10.280 --> 00:06:12.240
Sinan is so elegant and charming.

00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:15.280
Unlike you, who only deserves to marry a madman.

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:18.440
You're insane!

00:06:20.040 --> 00:06:21.400
How dare you hit me!

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:24.720
Guards!

00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:34.240
Kill her for me!

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:35.960
I'd like to see who dares.

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:06.520
Liu Silin? How did he get here?

00:07:07.040 --> 00:07:09.280
Wasn't he poisoned? The young master looks quite spirited.

00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:10.960
Seems he's in good shape.

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:13.280
Brother, why are you here?

00:07:13.480 --> 00:07:15.610
For such a grand engagement ceremony,

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:17.260
of course I had to come.

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:21.280
Since the young master has graced us with his presence,

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:23.080
Shuyun is naturally delighted.

00:07:23.840 --> 00:07:30.040
But making such a grand affair out of an engagement ceremony,

00:07:31.320 --> 00:07:34.680
Miss Xu truly lives up to being the commander's daughter.

00:07:34.840 --> 00:07:37.040
Young master, there's something you don't know.

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:38.720
Just now, this maid...

00:07:40.840 --> 00:07:44.280
The young mistress just slapped me across the face.

00:07:44.840 --> 00:07:47.240
How should we settle this matter?

00:07:52.760 --> 00:07:54.440
How dare you!

00:07:54.960 --> 00:07:56.720
You even dared to hit Miss Xu.

00:08:00.280 --> 00:08:03.160
I'll deal with you properly when we get back.

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:08.440
Young Master, since you're here,

00:08:08.440 --> 00:08:10.500
why not have a drink before you leave?

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:13.560
We'll be family soon.

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:16.880
I appreciate your kindness, Miss Xu,

00:08:17.160 --> 00:08:18.490
but I'm not interested.

00:08:19.560 --> 00:08:21.160
Who's so bold

00:08:21.280 --> 00:08:24.720
to disrupt the wedding at my commander's mansion?

00:08:35.400 --> 00:08:37.320
Making me lose face like this!

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:39.799
Where do you think you're going?

00:08:39.960 --> 00:08:41.000
Catch them!

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:41.960
Commander,

00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:43.559
please let it go.

00:08:43.600 --> 00:08:44.680
Let them leave.

00:08:45.280 --> 00:08:48.340
They are my elder brother and sister-in-law after all.

00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:51.560
They hit my daughter,

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:54.290
which is a slap in the face to my authority.

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:57.040
For your father's sake,

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:58.880
I'll give you a way out.

00:09:00.160 --> 00:09:02.600
Toast every guest here

00:09:02.960 --> 00:09:04.560
as an apology.

00:09:10.840 --> 00:09:11.720
Commander,

00:09:14.320 --> 00:09:16.000
please don't hold it against my brother.

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:17.860
I'll drink this cup on his behalf.

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:21.120
Liu Sinan.

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:23.240
Who do you think you are?

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:25.170
You have no right to speak here.

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:28.120
If it weren't for your Liu family's reputation,

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:29.680
you son of a servant,

00:09:29.800 --> 00:09:32.560
you'd never dream of becoming my Commander's son-in-law.

00:09:32.560 --> 00:09:36.120
You might tolerate others bullying your fiancée,

00:09:36.560 --> 00:09:38.000
but I won't stand for it.

00:09:38.360 --> 00:09:40.890
And neither will the Commander's household.

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:42.560
If you don't drink,

00:09:42.640 --> 00:09:46.240
